<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="break-off">break off</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>中断；折断；断绝：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He broke off speaking to answer the telephone. 
他中断了谈话去接电话。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The back part of the plane broke off. 
飞机的后部折断了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Wesley broke off with his girlfriend. 
卫斯理和他的女朋友断绝了关系。</p></div></div>